These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-1::.
House: art-deco, colonial, townhouse
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, hip-hop, techno
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, polish, russian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, pall-mall, vegafina
 1. the fonseca-smoker and the fan hip-hop have different parity positions##9
 2. the fan d&b is somewhere to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##5
 3. the fonseca-smoker is not the colonial house##6
 4. the malaysian is on the left of the russian##1
 5. the fan d&b and the colonial house have different parity positions##9
 6. the fan techno is the townhouse house##1
 7. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the fan techno##1
 9. the fan hip-hop and the townhouse house have different parity positions##9
10. the malaysian is the fan hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Job           | art-deco | colonial | townhouse    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b       | hip-hop   | techno   |
| Nationality   | polish    | malaysian | russian  |
| Transport     | vegafina   | pall-mall       | fonseca |

