.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, country, hip-hop
City: rome, liverpool, san-francisco
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, satire, western
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, ship, subway
1. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the right of the fan hip-hop##5
2. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the fan classical##8
3. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
4. the person watching drama movies and the fan country have the same parity positions##9
5. the person traveling to rome and the fan classical have different parity positions##9
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is in the middle##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
8. the person watching western movies is the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3     |
| Food          | hip-hop  | classical         | country |
| Hobby         | rome | san-francisco | liverpool   |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | western       | drama     |
| Transport     | boat       | ship          | subway    |

