.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, bolivar, chaman
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, martial-arts, zombie
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, sunflower, azalea
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, scooter, trike
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the chaman-smoker##8
2. the person who growssunflower is somewhere to the right of the bolivar-smoker##5
3. the chaman-smoker is the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
5. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person who growsmarigold##5
6. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the person who growssunflower##8
8. the alhambra-smoker and the person who growsazalea have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | alhambra | bolivar | chaman |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie      | crime   | martial-arts  |
| Music-Genre   | azalea        | marigold  | sunflower         |
| Transport     | trike       | bike    | scooter       |

