.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-4::.
City: hamburg, new-york, miami
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, fishing, puzzles
3 different pets are kept: frog, horse, rabbit
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, train, van
1. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person traveling to hamburg have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is in the middle##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
8. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the right of the person traveling to miami##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |       3       |
| Job           | new-york    | hamburg | miami |
| Movie-Genre   | puzzles | fishing       | rock-climbing     |
| Pet           | horse        | rabbit      | frog          |
| Transport     | train        | van         | motorbike     |

