.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-5::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, june, september
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, skiing, snowboarding
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, thriller, zombie
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, german, indian
1. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
2. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##5
3. the indian is between the person who's sport is cricket and the canadian##2
4. the german is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##8
5. the person who's birthday is in november and the german have the same parity positions##9
6. the german is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5
7. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##8
8. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person watching thriller movies##8
9. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |
| Hobby         | june  | september   | november |
| Job           | skiing   | snowboarding | cricket |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie   | thriller  | spy     |
| Nationality   | canadian | indian    | german  |

