.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, milk
There 3 different types of food: avocado, cauliflower, cucumber
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, videographer, musician
3 different games are played: snooker, whist, canasta
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the coach is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
 3. the person eating cucumber is not the person playing canasta##6
 4. the person playing whist and the coach have different parity positions##9
 5. the person playing canasta is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is not the videographer##6
 7. the person drinking milk and the person eating cauliflower have different parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the videographer##5
 9. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the musician##5
10. the person eating cauliflower and the person drinking iced-tea have the same parity positions##9
11. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
12. the musician is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |      3      |
| Beverage    | iced-tea   | milk         | lemonade    |
| Food        | avocado    | cucumber     | cauliflower |
| Hobby       | coach | musician | videographer     |
| Transport   | snooker        | whist   | canasta         |

